Sentencas: A single layer solid oxide fuel cell composed of La2NiO4 and samarium dope ceria (SDC)(Li0.67Na0.33)(2)CO3 is fabricated and characterized.
Titulo: A single layer solid oxide fuel cell composed of La2NiO4 and doped curia-carbonate with H2 and methanol as fuels

Sentencas: La2NiO4 shows a K2NiF4 structure in an oxidizing atmosphere, and is decomposed to Ni and La2O3 in a reducing atmosphere at the operating temperature of the cell.
Titulo: A single layer solid oxide fuel cell composed of La2NiO4 and doped curia-carbonate with H2 and methanol as fuels

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of the composite material increases with the increase of the content of La2NiO4.
Titulo: A single layer solid oxide fuel cell composed of La2NiO4 and doped curia-carbonate with H2 and methanol as fuels

Sentencas: At 700 degrees C, the single cell composed of 30 wt.% La2NiO4 and 70 wt.% SDC-(Li0.67Na0.33)(2)CO3 exhibits the highest power output of 340 and 331 mW cm(-2) with H-2 and methanol as fuels, respectively.
Titulo: A single layer solid oxide fuel cell composed of La2NiO4 and doped curia-carbonate with H2 and methanol as fuels

Sentencas: The stability of the cell with H-2 and methanol as the fuels is investigated.
Titulo: A single layer solid oxide fuel cell composed of La2NiO4 and doped curia-carbonate with H2 and methanol as fuels
